The Amazon young are given a weapon and are allowed to accompany their older sisters in battle but need to prove themselves before they can be initiated into one of the Amazon war mysteries. With the blessing of their queens, warriors receive a new calling, along with better training and equipment. Initiation rites require specific buildings to be constructed first.
